            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Every <fr:link href="jms-00KS.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="jms-00KS" type="local">section-retraction pair</fr:link> determines an <fr:link href="jms-00LA.xml" title="Idempotent function" addr="jms-00LA" type="local">idempotent</fr:link>. In particular, when <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="jms-00KS.xml" title="Section-retraction pair" addr="jms-00KS" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>, the composite <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\circ  r\colon  A\to  A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00LA.xml" title="Idempotent function" addr="jms-00LA" type="local">idempotent</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
